I was just thinking, we can define a trait in disks something like

```rust
trait UDisksWidgetBuilder {
    pub async fn widget_for_object(object: &udisks::Object) -> gtk::Widget;
    pub async fn widget_from_objects(objects: &[udisks::Object]) -> gtk::Widget;
}
```

This can then implemented for the `Client` so the caller can directly create widgets like `client.<corresponding_method>()`.

Just a suggestion, what do you think?
